nodes.text: A Gank backhanded the Sullustan journalist Den Dhur on the streets of the city–planet of Coruscant when Dhur inadvertently jostled the Gank while the journalist was inebriated. The Gank's partner, a member of the same species, then threatened the journalist with a vibroknife. The droid I-5YQ arrived on the scene, however, and frightened the Ganks away.
